---
title: Bot Runtime Architecture
---
flowchart LR
    TG[Telegram API] <--> GW[bot-gateway]

    subgraph gateway["Gateway responsibilities"]
        RL[rate limit]
        IDEMP[update idempotency]
        FSM[user session state]
        SIGN[sign internal requests]
    end

    GW --> RL
    GW --> IDEMP
    GW --> FSM
    GW --> SIGN

    SIGN --> BK[booking-service]
    SIGN --> PAY[payment-service]
    SIGN --> CAL[calendar-service]
    SIGN --> ADM[admin-service]

    BK --> DB[(PostgreSQL via PgBouncer)]
    PAY --> DB
    CAL --> DB
    ADM --> DB
    ANA[analytics-service] --> DB

    BK --> R[(Redis)]
    PAY --> R
    CAL --> R
    ADM --> R
    ANA --> R
    NOT[notification-service] --> R
    WK[worker-service] --> R

    R --> NOT
    R --> ANA
    R --> PAY
    R --> WK

    NOT --> TG

    DB --> AUD[audit schema]
    ADM --> OPS[DLQ replay and payment recovery]
